title: New Comics Week 12-24-08 pt 4
description:
This torrent contains another batch of new comics for this week that have not otherwise found their way to the Bay.

Included herein is the long awaited Ultimate Spider-man #129 (Ultimatum) and Ms Marvel #34 (Dark Reign) as well as a bunch of other books that have finally filtered down through the Holiday mayhem.

Thanks to the scanners who worked hard through it all to bring us these books, and to the original sources who shall remain nameless.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
